waveplot: 
	OpenGL .wav file waveform monitor for OpenGL 2.0+ compatible devices.
	No deprecated OpenGL functionality is used (i.e. no matrix stack or 
	fixed-function rendering calls). The shaders use GLSL 330.
	
	Features:
		- a linear algebra suite using SSE intrinsics (up to SSE4.2)
		- "inertial" mouse navigation, heads-up display
	
	Currently, only the Windows version compiles and works. 
